    "There must be a protagonist that is empathetic to the reader.",
    "That protagonist must face a high possibility of an outcome undesired by the protagonist and the reader.",
    "The quantity and quality (roughly in terms of expected probability) of ways of avoiding that undesired outcome are reduced.",
    "This suggests an adversarial planning process wherein the generator establishes the conditions for suspense in three stages of generation.",
